		<title>Postgres 2.0 Beta 3</title>
		<description>
			<![CDATA[
				<p>This beta 3 update of Postgres.app includes the following features:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>bugfix for dark mode (Thanks to Adam Hartford)</li>
				</ul>
				<p>This build includes 2 versions of PostgreSQL:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>PostgreSQL 9.6.1 (with PostGIS 2.3)</li>
					<li>PostgreSQL 9.5.5 (with PostGIS 2.2.3)</li>
				</ul>
			]]>
		</description>
